{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completionHandler:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^)()) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"animated"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The block executed after the animation finishes.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"completion"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","